This bootcamp will teach you the skills you need to become a full-stack web developer. You will learn the fundamentals of HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Node, Express, and MongoDB. You will also learn how to integrate the frontend and backend of a web application. By the end of the bootcamp, you will be able to build a complete web application from scratch.
